item.dc:creator: @moparisthebest Moparisthebest
item.description:
@moparisthebest wrote:

Better than looking at the bytecode of a given jar is taking the md5sum of it, because they have also been known to release two different clients with the same version number. So if you only look at the version number you could easily be caught with your pants down

Read full topic
